sentences: Valeria Cisternas (born 1 December 1986), better known by her stage name Tomasa Del Real, is a Chilean singer, composer, and reggaeton artist.
Tomasa was born in Iquique, Chile on December 1, 1986, to an upper-class family.
In 2015, due to growing success and demand as a performer, Del Real closed her tattoo shop, as she no longer had the time to attend to it.
Del Real released her first album Bien y Mal in March 2016.
Her album Bellaca del Año was released on May 18, 2018, via Nacional Records.
